videos.description: Off of a missed South Dakota State three-pointer, Oregon gets out on the fast break and Sabrina Ionescu lays it in on the other end.
videos.headline: Ionescu scores fast-break layup

videos.description: Sabrina Ionescu rips the ball away from Tylee Irwin, and on the other end, Ruthy Hebard corrals Ionescu's deflected pass and lays it in.
videos.headline: Ionescu's steal leads to Hebard layup
